data.content:
Danh từ
(thường pair of dividers)
chiếc compa đo góc

noun
plural -ers
[count] a thing that keeps two spaces or areas separate
Concrete barriers are used as highway dividers.
someone or something that causes people to disagree with one another
She has proven to be a divider of people.
He says that he's a uniter, not a divider.
dividers [plural] :a tool that consists of two pointed sticks joined at the top and that is used for measuring or marking lines and angles
a pair of dividers
